### Get ditto data
GET http://localhost:3000/pokemon/ditto

### Create a new pokemon
POST http://localhost:3000/pokemon
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pikachu",
  "type": "Electric",
  "level": 25,
  "moves": [
    "Thunder Shock",
    "Quick Attack",
    "Iron Tail",
    "Electro Ball"
  ]
}